      "Players will be able to customise their character, select their Hogwarts House, attend lessons, explore Hogwarts, and join the Duelling Club.",
      "The core of Magic Awakened's gameplay is a digital-collectible card-based RTS in which   spells are in the form of cards obtainable from gacha spins."
