      "Tom Marvolo Riddle (31 December 1926[17] \u2013 2 May 1998), later known as Lord Voldemort or, alternatively as You-Know-Who, the Dark Lord, or He-Who-Must-Not-Be-Named was an English half-blood[3] wizard considered to have been the most powerful and dangerous Dark Wizard of all time.",
